quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not expanded for you your breast
  94,2,And eased you of the burden
  94,3,Which weighed so heavily on your back
  94,4,And (have We not) exalted for you your renown
  94,5,"Then, surely, with hardship comes ease"
  94,6,"Surely, with hardship comes ease"
  94,7,"Therefore, when you are free (from one task), resume (another task)"
  94,8,And seek and strive to please your Lord